extendedInfo.description: Planning a move? CLICKandMOVE.com is the world's easiest way to get competitive moving quotes. One entry-multiple moving estimates. Now you can easily do your own furniture inventory online and submit to multiple movers for bids. Choose your moving companies from our extensive list of AMSA PRO MOVERS. Whether you need a small local mover or a national van line, you are assured of competitive rates AND reliable moving services. CLICK.and.MOVE, one inventory, multiple quotes.
